features: Give their accomplishment the distinction and recognition it deserves by printing their awards on these Abstract Stars Foil Certificate Papers
Made from durable, lightweight 210 GSM paper, each blank certificate consists of elegant white parchment printed with a distinguished silver foil stamped border featured metallic stars
Each pack contains 15 standard letter-size sheets that measure 8.5” by 11” and are printer-ready right out of the packaging
Print awards, diplomas and more with your own printer on these blank, customizable sheets
For a complete presentation pair them with our foil stamped certificate holders and seals
body.description: Whether it’s an award, a degree or another accomplishment, mark the milestone with a beautiful keepsake when you create a customized document using our 15-piece set of Abstract Stars Foil Certificate Paper. Each standard size sheet measures 8.5” by 11”, making them perfect for use with your home office printer. Made of cover stock paper, each white sheet is lightweight, durable and high-quality with an eye-catching star design running along the edge. Due to the count of this set, these are perfect for educational and professional purposes. Pair these sheets with our foil stamped certificate holders and seals to create a complete set. • Gartner Studios is a leader in creating do-it-yourself products to celebrate weddings, birthdays, graduations and more. Best known for our expansive line of party goods and stationery products, we design, manufacture and distribute celebration assortments with a simple goal in mind: to inspire you to celebrate everyday life & events in style. From design concept to finished product, we give our customers the style and trends they truly love!
